COMMANDS INDEX

Syntax: commands

Lists all player commands in five columns. Type help to open the
categorized help menu for topics and policies.

Common commands:
  Movement: north, south, east, west, up, down, look
  Character: score, eq, worn, inventory, advance, improve
  Combat: kill, flee, dodge, parry, stance, rest
  Social: say, emote, whisper, introduce, greet, ooc
  Communication: radio, telepathy, tell, mail

Type help <command> for any command that exists in the game.

SEE ALSO: getting-started, syntax, help
